summary: An orc girl with a pretty face!? Saved in Helgen keep after being unbound.
descriptionHtml:
I thought I\'d upload a save of my pretty orc girl Grylla. No cheats or anything, just a save at level one in helgen keep after the hands are unbound.

To achieve the purty face these mods are installed:
Thepal\'s nudes http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=70
Amazing Smooth Females Complete by Zalzama http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=140
Beauty Faces by necKros http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=1329
author: Kelticfury
